title: KyleCoaching Base Training Camp
description: Join Chuck, Dana, and fellow KyleCoaching athletes for our winter base camp in Clermont Florida.  the purpose of this camp is to give you the opportunity to gain valuable base mileage this winter.  Instead of hours on the trainer racing up points on Zwift or buckets of sweet with your favorite Sufferfest video, join us for miles of riding in beautiful Clermont Florida.

title: Sunshine GP-Powell TT and Ice Cream Hill RR
Vel-o-Dyssey LC Tri Shop and Team Walker Ride 2017
description: Fun-ride for riders of any level to participate in.  There will be two different distance options, at 80 miles and 40 miles.  Come out and join in on the fun, but make sure you get signed up early, because the registration limit for the event is 200 riders.
course:
Here is a link to the map of the course: http://www.strava.com/routes/7925242 .  2 Routes   A Group 80 Miles  2 Rest stops.  (1 stop at mile 30 & 2nd stop at mile 57)
     B Group 40 Miles.   1 Rest stop at mile 20.
notes: This is not a  race, but a ride.  You will be debriefed before the ride about the rules of the ride.

title: Bill Bone Saving Limbs Ride

address.street: Datura and Flagler along the waterfront

description: Charity Bike Ride and Family Fun Ride.
course: Bike ride is 50 miles along the Atlantic Ocean. Ride is on open roads. Family Fun Ride is 3 miles on bike path that runs along the Intracoastal Waterway
notes: Ride starts at 7:30 am. Family Fun Ride at 9:00am
directions: Ride Start is at Datura and Flagler, downtown West Palm Beach.
